<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_Dojo_Form_SubForm decorator ContentPane renders a name attribute in the surrounding div with the value of the subform name. This is not XHTML compliant, as there is no name attribute for divs.</p>

<p>Here is an example that produces this behavior:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$form = new Zend_Dojo_Form();
$subform = new Zend_Dojo_Form_SubForm();
$subform-&gt;addElement('text', 'test');
$form-&gt;addSubForm($subform, 'test');

echo $form;
</code></pre>

